name: BlockChain Barcodes 09 - Fear Of Missing Out
description: lockChain Barcodes are a collection of phrases common in our community that have been translated from an ASCI string into binary and then represented as a Code 128 Standard barcode that can be read with a barcode scanning app. Included in the footer is the original string to juxtapose the digitization of the human experience and consider the abstraction of data into art.
